                     <h2>WHAT IS A FLAVOR EMULSION</h2>
                     <p>Emulsions are made through high-shear processes where we minimize the droplets of the oils within our flavor oil and emulsifier mix, usually a gum acacia. Through this process, we made the oils into highly concentrated, water-soluble flavors that are great for high-heat applications.</p>
                  </div>
