                     <h2>STARTING USAGE</h2>
                     <p>Emulsions are water-soluble and highly concentrated flavors, for that reason, starting usage is 0.1% - 0.5%. by weight. Experimentation is needed. Feel free to call us for some tips. If the flavor tastes good and dissipates after 3 to 5 seconds, it's perfect!</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
